    "CircAD builds a predictive model based on known experimentally verified associations between circRNAs and diseases and conducts experimental verification.",
    "CircDA includes dataset collation, heterogeneous network construction, classifier construction based on the Tumarkov neural network, HCC-based RT-qPCR experimental verification, and online server construction.",
